# Lesson XI excercise solutions

## 210

1. Caesar was a bold leader of the Romans

2. The power of his leader was big

3. All the soldiers loved Caesar earnestly because he often defeated enemies.

4. The hardships of the soldiers in battle were often severe.

5. The enemies were many and eager and they were throwing many spears at the Romans.

6. But our cohorts did not flee because of common danger.

7. They fought for Rome bravely.

8. This war was short. 
